headline: Agoda and ASEAN launch 'A Destination for Every Dream' Campaign this ASEAN Day
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda, in partnership with the Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN), has launched the 'A Destination for Every Dream' campaign to inspire and promote travel within the ASEAN region.
